# API Usage

Run locally:
$ python app.py

Endpoints:
GET    /tasks              -> list all tasks
GET    /tasks?q=<term>     -> search tasks
GET    /tasks/<id>         -> get a single task
POST   /tasks              -> create task, JSON body: {"description":"..."}
PUT    /tasks/<id>         -> replace task description, JSON body: {"description":"..."}
POST   /tasks/<id>/complete-> mark task complete
DELETE /tasks/<id>         -> delete a task
